p\", \"from\": 4525, \"to\": 4556}, {\"ngram\": \"medical misogyny\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"pay\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"feminised industries\", \"from\": 4605, \"to\": 4625}, {\"ngram\": \"makingreproductive rights sacrosanctandlegislating\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"gendered violence\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The female generation who moshed were always in it for a good time, not a long time - but we know tangible material changes that we make are hard to undo.\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The female generation\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"a good time\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4770}, {\"ngram\": \"tangible material changes\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So do the far right, so they try to legislate women's containment and terrify the younger women - the Khelifs, the daughters of Vance voters - about the price of stepping out of line.\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 5042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4987, \"end\": 4992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"score\": 0.9972326444632419, \"rank\": 0.002775035030090285, \"text\": \"Vance\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zebulon_Baird_Vance\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women's containment\", \"from\": 4905, \"to\": 4924}, {\"ngram\": \"the younger women\", \"from\": 4937, \"to\": 4954}, {\"ngram\": \"the Khelifs\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"the daughters\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 5008, \"to\": 5017}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Humiliation.\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Humiliation\", \"from\": 5043, 