b\", \"from\": 5459, \"to\": 5466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let them cry about it; keep boxing.\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lesson that generation X learned from one of our seminal texts - the nuclear anxiety movieWarGames- that instructs us how to fight the right's gender war, whether you are a childless cat lady, a harassed champion boxer, or a suffering stay-at-home wife.\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lesson\", \"from\": 5514, \"to\": 5522}, {\"ngram\": \"that generation X\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5540}, {\"ngram\": \"our seminal texts\", \"from\": 5561, \"to\": 5578}, {\"ngram\": \"the nuclear anxiety movieWarGames-\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5615}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5631, \"to\": 5633}, {\"ngram\": \"the right's gender war\", \"from\": 5647, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"a childless cat lady\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5707}, {\"ngram\": \"a harassed champion boxer\", \"from\": 5709, \"to\": 5734}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 5759, \"to\": 5763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only winning move is not to play.\\\"\", \"from\": 5771, \"to\": 5810, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only winning move\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Badham is a Guardian Australia columnist\", \"from\": 5812, \"to\": 5856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5812, \"end\": 5822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Van_Badham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Van Badham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Van_Badham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Van_Badham\"}, {\"begin\": 5828, \"end\": 5846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guardian Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso